<h1>Problem 1063 - 2011 IMOSL, G2, G</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 8</h2>
<p>Let \(A_1A_2A_3A_4\) be a non-cyclic quadrilateral. Let \(O_1\) and \(r_1\) be the circumcentre and the circumradius of the triangle \(A_2A_3A_4\). Define \(O_2,O_3,O_4\) and \(r_2,r_3,r_4\) in a similar way. Prove that
\[\frac{1}{O_1A_1^2-r_1^2}+\frac{1}{O_2A_2^2-r_2^2}+\frac{1}{O_3A_3^2-r_3^2}+\frac{1}{O_4A_4^2-r_4^2}=0.\]</p>
